2. Factory Method - Define interface for creating objects

5. Prototype - Create objects by copying

These patterns although classic, modern languages provide many syntactic sugar. Understanding principles important!

note.title: Programming Language Comparison
note.content:
Compared different programming languages characteristics and applicable scenarios.

Python:
- Concise syntax, gentle learning curve
- Powerful data science and AI ecosystem
- Execution efficiency general but development efficiency high

Go:
- Excellent concurrency performance
- Fast compilation, easy deployment
- Concise syntax, clear error handling

Rust:
- Memory safety guarantee
- Zero-cost abstractions
- Steep learning curve but worth it

Choose appropriate tools important!

6. Test coverage

Code review not just finding errors, but knowledge sharing and team growth opportunity.

High-quality code is team foundation! ğŸ”

Weekend stayed home finished "The Kite Runner", touching story.

Novel through Afghan boy Amir's growth experiences, shows friendship, betrayal, redemption themes. Hosseini's narrative mastery, plot rises and falls.

Most impressive "For you, a thousand times over" echoes in mind. Friendship sometimes so pure and deep.

Recommend everyone read! ğŸ“š

note.title: Agile Development Practice
note.content:
Team started implementing agile development methods, effects significant.

Main changes:
1. Two-week iteration cycles
2. Daily standups maintain sync
3. User stories drive development
4. Continuous integration and deployment
5. Iteration end retrospectives

Team response speed significantly improved, product quality guaranteed. Agile not silver bullet but suitable for rapidly changing environments.

Good processes let team more efficient! âš¡

note.title: Coffee Tasting Experience
note.content:
Attended coffee tasting workshop, learned lots of professional knowledge.

Learned:
1. Coffee bean origins and varieties differences
2. Roast degree influence on flavor
3. Brewing method choices
4. Professional coffee tasting terms
5. Different origin characteristics

From Ethiopian Yirgacheffe to Colombian Geisha, each coffee has unique charm.

Coffee culture really profound! â˜•
